[{"name":"however","pos":"adverb","content":"<div class=\"entry\" sk=\"however: :0\" htag=\"section\" id=\"however\" hlength=\"7\" hclass=\"entry\" sum=\"913\" idm_id=\"000029071\"><div class=\"top-container\"><div class=\"top-g\" id=\"however_topg_1\"><div class=\"webtop\"><h1 class=\"headword\" htag=\"h1\" ox3000=\"y\" id=\"however_h_1\" opal_written=\"y\" opal_spoken=\"y\" random=\"y\" hclass=\"headword\">however</h1> <span class=\"pos\" hclass=\"pos\" htag=\"span\">adverb</span><div class=\"symbols\" hclass=\"symbols\" htag=\"div\"><a href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/wordlists/oxford3000-5000?dataset=english&amp;list=ox3000&amp;level=a1\"><span class=\"ox3ksym_a1\">&nbsp;</span></a><a href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/wordlists/opal?dataset=english&amp;list=opal_written&amp;level=sublist_2\"><span class=\"opal_symbol\" href=\"OPAL_Written::Sublist_2\">OPAL W</span></a><a href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/wordlists/opal?dataset=english&amp;list=opal_spoken&amp;level=sublist_4\"><span class=\"opal_symbol\" href=\"OPAL_Spoken::Sublist_4\">OPAL S</span></a></div><span class=\"phonetics\"> <div class=\"phons_br\" hclass=\"phons_br\" wd=\"however\" htag=\"div\" geo=\"br\"><div class=\"sound audio_play_button pron-uk icon-audio\" data-src-mp3=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/media/english/uk_pron/h/how/howev/however__gb_2.mp3\" data-src-ogg=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/media/english/uk_pron_ogg/h/how/howev/however__gb_2.ogg\" title=\"however pronunciation\n                    English\" style=\"cursor: pointer\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</div><span class=\"phon\">/haʊˈevə(r)/</span></div> <div class=\"phons_n_am\" hclass=\"phons_n_am\" wd=\"however\" htag=\"div\" geo=\"n_am\"><div class=\"sound audio_play_button pron-us icon-audio\" data-src-mp3=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/media/english/us_pron/h/how/howev/however__us_2.mp3\" data-src-ogg=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/media/english/us_pron_ogg/h/how/howev/however__us_2.ogg\" title=\"however pronunciation\n                    American\" style=\"cursor: pointer\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</div><span class=\"phon\">/haʊˈevər/</span></div></span></div><a class=\"responsive_display_inline_on_smartphone link-right\" href=\"#relatedentries\">\n                            jump to other results\n                        </a></div></div><ol class=\"senses_multiple\" htag=\"ol\"><li class=\"sense\" sensenum=\"1\" hclass=\"sense\" id=\"however_sng_3\" ox3000=\"y\" cefr=\"a1\" htag=\"li\"><a class=\"open oup_icons\" title=\"Add to My Word Lists\"><span class=\"star-btn\" aria-hidden=\"true\">​</span></a><span class=\"sensetop\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"sensetop\"><div class=\"symbols\" htag=\"div\" hclass=\"symbols\"><a href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/wordlists/oxford3000-5000?dataset=english&amp;list=ox3000&amp;level=a1\"><span class=\"ox3ksym_a1\">&nbsp;</span></a></div></span> <span class=\"def\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"def\">used to introduce a statement that contrasts with something that has just been said</span><ul class=\"examples\" hclass=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">He was feeling bad. He went to work, however, and tried to concentrate.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">We thought the figures were correct. However, we have now discovered some errors.</span></li></ul><div class=\"collapse\" hclass=\"collapse\" htag=\"div\"><span class=\"unbox\" id=\"however_unbox_1\" unbox=\"langbank\"><span class=\"box_title\">Language Bank <span class=\"closed\">however</span></span><span class=\"body\"><span class=\"unbox\">however</span><span class=\"unbox\">Ways of saying ‘but’</span><ul class=\"bullet\"><li class=\"li\"><ul class=\"examples\" hclass=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Politicians have promised to improve road safety. So far, <span class=\"eb\">however</span>, little has been achieved.</span></li></ul></li><li class=\"li\"><ul class=\"examples\" hclass=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\"><span class=\"eb\">Despite</span> clear evidence from road safety studies, no new measures have been introduced.</span></li></ul></li><li class=\"li\"><ul class=\"examples\" hclass=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Politicians have promised to improve road safety. <span class=\"eb\">In spite of this</span>/<span class=\"eb\">Despite this</span>, little has been achieved so far.</span></li></ul></li><li class=\"li\"><ul class=\"examples\" hclass=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\"><span class=\"eb\">Although</span> politicians have promised to improve road safety, little has been achieved so far.</span></li></ul></li><li class=\"li\"><ul class=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\" hclass=\"examples\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Some politicians claim that the new transport policy has been a success. <span class=\"eb\">In fact</span>, it has been a total disaster. </span></li></ul></li><li class=\"li\"><ul class=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\" hclass=\"examples\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Government campaigns have had a measure of success, <span class=\"eb\">but the fact remains that</span> large numbers of accidents are still caused by careless drivers.</span></li></ul></li></ul><span class=\"xrefs\" xt=\"langbankat\" hclass=\"xrefs\" htag=\"span\"><span class=\"prefix\"><span class=\"esc\">language bank</span> at</span> <span class=\"xr-g\" href=\"nevertheless_unbox_1\" bord=\"n\"><span class=\"xh\">nevertheless</span></span></span></span></span></div>          \n</li><li class=\"sense\" htag=\"li\" ox3000=\"y\" cefr=\"b2\" id=\"however_sng_1\" hclass=\"sense\" sensenum=\"2\"><a class=\"open oup_icons\" title=\"Add to My Word Lists\"><span class=\"star-btn\" aria-hidden=\"true\">​</span></a><span class=\"sensetop\" hclas